### 6. Sort Array in Ascending Order

**Problem:** Sort an array in ascending order.

```java
import java.util.Arrays;

class SortAscending {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = {4, 2, 7, 1, 9};
        Arrays.sort(arr);

        for (int num : arr)
            System.out.print(num + " ");
    }
}
```

---

### 7. Sort Array in Descending Order

**Problem:** Sort an array in descending order.

```java
import java.util.Arrays;

class SortDescending {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Integer[] arr = {4, 2, 7, 1, 9};
        Arrays.sort(arr, java.util.Collections.reverseOrder());

        for (int num : arr)
            System.out.print(num + " ");
    }
}
```

